<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>outcomestar — Every outcome. One star.</title>
<meta name="description" content="One longitudinal record for your child's whole journey — academics, athletics, activities, applications. From first milestones to college admission.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:wght@500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
<style is:global>
:root{--navy:#201868;--orange:#F07800;--paper:#FAFAF7;--gray:#7A8A9E;--ink:#1a1a2e}
*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:Lora,Georgia,serif;color:var(--navy);margin:0}
.wrap{max-width:1020px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
.topbar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E2D9;background:#fff}
.topbar nav{display:flex;gap:18px;font-size:14px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.topbar nav a{color:var(--navy);text-decoration:none}
.topbar nav a.cta-in{color:#fff;background:var(--navy);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600}
.topbar nav a.cta-up{color:#fff;background:var(--orange);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600}
.btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--orange);color:#fff;font-weight:600;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;border:0;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer}
.hero{padding:64px 0 48px;text-align:center}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(32px,5.5vw,54px);line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.hero h1 span{color:var(--orange)}
.hero p{max-width:640px;margin:18px auto 30px;font-size:18px;color:#4A5563}
.rule{width:110px;border-bottom:3px solid var(--orange);margin:22px auto}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:22px;padding:36px 0 20px}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #E3E7ED;border-radius:14px;padding:26px}
.card h3{font-size:19px;margin-bottom:8px}
.card p{margin:0;color:#4A5563;font-size:14.5px}
.band{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:56px 24px;margin-top:48px}
.band h2{color:#fff;font-size:30px}
.band p{color:#C9C6E4;max-width:620px;margin:14px auto 26px}
footer{border-top:1px solid #E5E2D9;margin-top:0;padding:26px 20px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);background:var(--paper)}
footer a{color:var(--navy);text-decoration:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="topbar">
  <a href="https://outcomestar.app/"><img src="/outcomestar_logo_primary.png" alt="outcomestar" style="height:40px"></a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
    <a href="/insights">Insights</a>
    <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    <a href="/portal" class="cta-in">Sign in</a>
    <a href="/signup" class="cta-up">Create account</a>
  </nav>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Every outcome.<br><span>One star.</span></h1>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p>One longitudinal record for your child's whole journey &mdash; academics, athletics, arts, leadership, and service &mdash; organized from first milestones through college applications, so senior fall is an export, not a scramble.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/signup">Get started</a>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card"><h3>Five pillars, one record</h3><p>Personal, Academics, Extracurricular, Career, and Higher Education &mdash; every course, test, race, recital, rank, and role captured once and reused everywhere.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Applications that fill themselves</h3><p>Generate filled college application forms, tailored resumes, and comprehensive reports directly from your child's verified record.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>A website that grows up</h3><p>A family memory book at 5, a developmental portfolio at 10, a professional launchpad at 16 &mdash; privacy guardrails enforced at every age, in English and your home language.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Athletics, tracked properly</h3><p>Personal records, time standards, and progress analytics &mdash; recruitment-ready data instead of scattered screenshots.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Built by a parent</h3><p>Created for one family's road to college and opened to yours. Your data stays yours &mdash; export any time.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Private by default</h3><p>Child sites use first-name-only public pages, nondescript links, and no-index protection. Law first, parent second, child by age.</p></div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="band">
  <h2>Founding cohort now open</h2>
  <p>Founding families shape the product and lock in founding pricing.</p>
  <a class="btn" href="/signup">Create your account</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <a href="/user-agreement">Terms of Service</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
  <div style="margin-top:6px">&copy; 2026 SRJ Consulting &amp; Services LLC &middot; outcomestar.app &middot; Every outcome. One star.</div>
</footer>

